2026-04-29T06:56:36.8476307Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-04-29T06:56:36.8477155Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-04-29T06:56:36.8477969Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-04-29T06:56:36.8478953Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-04-29T06:56:36.8479923Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-29T06:56:36.8481040Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-29T06:56:36.8482032Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-29T06:56:36.8483013Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-29T06:56:36.8484171Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-04-29T06:56:36.8485127Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-04-29T06:56:36.8485876Z 33    -->
2026-04-29T06:56:36.8486673Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-04-29T06:56:36.8487893Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:5-79
2026-04-29T06:56:36.8489144Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:22-76
2026-04-29T06:56:36.8490328Z 35    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_EXACT_ALARM" />
