2026-04-29T06:56:36.9769450Z 45    <!--
2026-04-29T06:56:36.9769803Z 46        Foreground service used to keep the Pomodoro countdown alive when
2026-04-29T06:56:36.9770136Z 47        the app is backgrounded. Without this, a viewModelScope coroutine
2026-04-29T06:56:36.9770473Z 48        is cancelled as soon as the user switches apps and the completion
2026-04-29T06:56:36.9770774Z 49        notification is never shown. The timer is declared as a
2026-04-29T06:56:36.9771324Z 50        mediaPlayback foreground service because Samsung One UI suppresses
